# 🌐 Resume Generator - Live Public Access

## ✅ Your Resume Generator is Ready!

### 🚀 Instant Deployment Options

#### Option 1: CodeSandbox (Instant & Free)
1. Go to [CodeSandbox.io](https://codesandbox.io)
2. Click "Create Sandbox"
3. Choose "Import from GitHub" 
4. Upload this project
5. **Instant public URL!**

#### Option 2: Replit (Free & Easy)
1. Go to [Replit.com](https://replit.com)
2. Click "Create Repl"
3. Choose "Import from GitHub"
4. Upload this project
5. Click "Run"
6. **Public URL generated automatically!**

#### Option 3: Glitch (Simple)
1. Go to [Glitch.com](https://glitch.com)
2. Click "New Project"
3. Choose "Import from GitHub"
4. **Live URL in seconds!**

